snippet.textDisplay: Shuja Haider! you must be a truly blessed man by Allah to write such lyrics. Today for the first time I heard this song with subtitles on and I was stunned. You have described Allah's greatness so powerfully that with every line you realize how supreme He is and how little we are in front of Him. The mentioning of Allah's names and attributes is beautiful ( especially 'the Knower of Unspoken Prayers' ). This song is a beautiful combination of Allah's praise, dua, asking for forgiveness, seeking His help, repentance and humbleness. Hats off to you. May Allah reward you.
